{"id":149876,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：世界人口今年将突破70亿/","date":"2011-05-05T00:00:30Z","modified":"2011-05-05T00:00:30Z","title":"简讯：世界人口今年将突破70亿","content":"<div>\n<p>最新联合国报告预言，世界总人口数将在今年10月31日突破70亿大关。</p>\n<p>报告还预言，全球人口总数在2050年将能达到93.1亿，比此前预计的水平多1.6亿。</p>\n<p>报告还提出，到本世纪末，全球人口总数将突破100亿。</p>\n<p>而中国人口数则将呈下降趋势，预计到世纪末将降至10亿以下。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/05/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Z6nuPgDEbaAa6ObcvJTaBzP-PgM/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Z6nuPgDEbaAa6ObcvJTaBzP-PgM/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Z6nuPgDEbaAa6ObcvJTaBzP-PgM/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Z6nuPgDEbaAa6ObcvJTaBzP-PgM/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/SG0Ex_BdWEA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[11846]}